<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{ app_title }}</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700;900&display=swap');

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: #0a0a0a;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .bg {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 20% 20%, rgba(99,102,241,0.15) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 80% 80%, rgba(16,185,129,0.1) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 50% 50%, rgba(139,92,246,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .grid {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 60px 60px;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .container {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      width: 90%;
    }

    .status-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      background: rgba(16,185,129,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.3);
      color: #10b981;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .dot {
      width: 7px;
      height: 7px;
      background: #10b981;
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
      50% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scale(0.8); }
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 8vw, 5rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    h1 .grad {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #6b7280;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .stack {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }

    .chip {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: #9ca3af;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 0.45rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .chip:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    }

    .chip .icon { font-size: 0.95rem; }

    .divider {
      width: 60px;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.15), transparent);
      margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    }

    footer {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #374151;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bg"></div>
  <div class="grid"></div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="status-pill">
      <span class="dot"></span>
      Deployed Successfully
    </div>

    <h1>Built with<br /><span class="grad">Infrastructure as Code</span></h1>

    <p>
      Provisioned on AWS with Terraform.<br />
      Configured and deployed with Ansible.
    </p>

    <div class="stack">
      <span class="chip"><span class="icon">⚡</span> Terraform</span>
      <span class="chip"><span class="icon">🤖</span> Ansible</span>
      <span class="chip"><span class="icon">☁️</span> AWS EC2</span>
      <span class="chip"><span class="icon">🌐</span> Nginx</span>
      <span class="chip"><span class="icon">🐧</span> Amazon Linux 2</span>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <footer>{{ ansible_date_time.date }} &nbsp;·&nbsp; {{ app_title }}</footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>